{"tid":633777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近3年逾百警員被捕　休班警佔過半","createTime":"2018-04-18T15:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T01:50:35.000Z","uid":4517,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c611deb3abb1726c0accd0bdfe72fc53b86b40c8","tid":633777,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:06:59.000Z","msg":"警務人員操守近年備受關注。警務署回覆立法會財委會議員的數據顯示，2015至2017年每年分別有35、43及29名警員被捕，當中各年分別有22、23及23名屬休班警。全體被捕警員中，這三年分別有19、34及18人是被警方拘捕。此外，每年分別有16、9及11名警員被其他執法部門拘捕，例如廉政公署及海關。<br />\n<br />\n被警方拘捕的警員中，2015至2017年分別各有15、21及15人，涉嫌干犯警隊定義為罪行性質屬較嚴重的刑事案件，當中19人涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢／打鬥、刑事毀壞及破壞公眾體統、遊蕩等罪行，有7人涉嫌傷人及嚴重毆打、6人涉嫌雜項盜竊。涉嫌非禮、詐騙或店舖盜竊的，各有5人；涉嫌強姦、襲警、刑事恐嚇或車輛內盜竊，則各有1人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180418/s00001/1524063240071?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180418%2Fs00001%2F1524063240071%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=o%2FPBgnZAqpsRyg6bO2uhdMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=7fd9baf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180418%2Fs00001%2F1524063240071%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=29363017\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180418/s00001/1524063240071?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"3a4b34a85c00d5c47e8901a21c499951ab0b46b1","tid":633777,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"GOALLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLL"},{"pid":"e1c8311c99cd29215f5f1963b3b5e1cc894da4a4","tid":633777,"uid":119769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61173c7f3ce233d9786b501fedd1ff4ced41c5d3","tid":633777,"uid":36551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"派彩作實<br />\n官方宣佈休班警大勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c316e83462c22b03440dca2f4